text: DuckDuckGo is a search engine made by Gabriel Weinberg. It stresses that it does not collect information about users like Google does, and keeps data private. It headquarters is in Paoli, Pennsylvania, United States. As of March 2020, it received 56,256,596 searches every day. ==References== == Other websites == * Category:2008 establishments in the United States Category:Companies based in Pennsylvania Category:American search engines
title: DuckDuckGo
